name: GlycolyticOscillation (dysts)
equations: GlycolyticOscillation system (see dysts package for equations)
description_simple: A model of feedback in glycolytic reactions. Based on the Monod–Wyman–Changeux model.
description_complex: A chaotic dynamical system imported from the dysts package. This system exhibits complex, sensitive dynamics characteristic of deterministic chaos.
